            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%911%E4%BA%BF%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%AF%E6%85%A2%E9%98%BB%E8%82%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%911%E4%BA%BF%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%AF%E6%85%A2%E9%98%BB%E8%82%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我国有近1亿人是慢阻肺人群#</span></a>】慢阻肺全称是“慢性阻塞性肺疾病”，主要表现为慢性支气管炎和肺气肿。目前，我国已经有接近1亿人是慢阻肺人群，它也跃升为我国排名第3的单病致死原因。空气中的灰霾和粉尘对气道也是一种刺激，慢阻肺患者出门可以戴口罩👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4982855194050647" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1hl624mub5tj60zk0k0adf02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/AcCwjp3jlx08bdJ3YWXm01041200Hz490E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709226879&amp;ssig=cnpc2nJlKc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/vOJ96HV5lx08bdJ3LKRW01041200mMXH0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709226879&amp;ssig=IeLCd1LjMv&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/OtAoFFP2lx08bdJ3QPh601041200dLOY0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709226879&amp;ssig=zl208A%2Bwlc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4982855194050647" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
